snippet.title: Amber Heard Grimaces When Asked About People Who Don't Believe Her Abuse Case Against Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Saturday, August 6, 2016 - Amber Heard shows up over an hour late for her deposition in her divorce and domestic abuse case against estranged husband Johnny Depp. The 30-year-old actress has postponed the deposition before, and this morning lawyers from both sides were there waiting for her. She is asked what she thinks of those people that don't believe her case against Johnny, and she makes a noticeable grimace in response.
